data.description: Come check out this meticulously maintained townhome! Conveniently located to all major Charlotte attractions, as well as the airport. Welcome inside to a large living space and generous sized kitchen with a walk in pantry. Upstairs you will find 3 ample sized bedrooms, including the master with its own private bathroom. Outside you will find a good sized backyard that is perfect for entertaining or even enjoying nice days out back relaxing. Property is convenient to the U.S. White Water Center.  Close to I-85, I-485 and I-77.  Also close to Charlotte-Douglas Airport, uptown Charlotte and Lake Norman.
